{
  "bookId": "laozi-boshu",
  "num": 64,
  "title": "第六十四章（輔物）",
  "author": "老子",
  "authorId": "Laozi",
  "dynasty": "周",
  "era": "周",
  "genre": "prose",
  "verses": [
    {
      "text": "亓安也，易持也。"
    },
    {
      "text": "亓未兆也，易謀也。"
    },
    {
      "text": "亓脆也，易判也。"
    },
    {
      "text": "亓微也，易散也。"
    },
    {
      "text": "為之於亓未有也。"
    },
    {
      "text": "治之於亓未亂也。"
    },
    {
      "text": "合抱之木，生於毫末。"
    },
    {
      "text": "九成之臺，作於羸土。"
    },
    {
      "text": "百仞之高，始於足下。"
    },
    {
      "text": "為之者敗之。"
    },
    {
      "text": "執之者失之。"
    },
    {
      "text": "是以聖人无為也。"
    },
    {
      "text": "故无敗也。"
    },
    {
      "text": "无執也。"
    },
    {
      "text": "故无失也。"
    },
    {
      "text": "民之從事也，恆於亓成而敗之。"
    },
    {
      "text": "故慎終若始，則无敗事矣。"
    },
    {
      "text": "是以聖人："
    },
    {
      "text": "欲不欲，而不貴難得之貨。"
    },
    {
      "text": "學不學，而復眾人之所過。"
    },
    {
      "text": "能輔萬物之自然，而弗敢為。"
    }
  ],
  "sections": {},
  "annotations": [],
  "layers": {
    "heshanggong": [
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-1",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 9,
          "end": 10
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "情欲禍患未有形兆時，易謀止也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-2",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 5,
          "start": 8,
          "end": 8
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "禍亂未動於朝，情欲未見於色，如脆弱易破除。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-3",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 28,
          "end": 29
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "其未彰著，微小易散去也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-4",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 5,
          "start": 8,
          "end": 8
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "欲有所為，當於未有萌芽之時塞其端也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-5",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 5,
          "start": 8,
          "end": 8
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "治身治國於未亂之時，當豫閉其門也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-6",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 1
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "從小成大。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-7",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 8,
          "start": 10,
          "end": 10
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "從卑立高。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-8",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 8,
          "start": 10,
          "end": 10
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "從近至遠。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-9",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 16,
          "start": 12,
          "end": 12
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "有為於事，廢於自然；有為於義，廢於仁；有為於色，廢於精神也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-10",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 16,
          "start": 12,
          "end": 12
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "執利遇患，執道全身，堅持不得，推讓反還。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-11",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 2,
          "start": 14,
          "end": 15
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "聖人不為華文，不為色利，不為殘賊，故無壞敗。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-12",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 2,
          "start": 29,
          "end": 30
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "聖人有德以教愚，有財以與貧，無所執藏，故無所失於人也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-13",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 16,
          "start": 12,
          "end": 12
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "從，為也。民之為事，常於功德幾成，而貪位好名，奢泰盈滿而自敗之也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-14",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 16,
          "start": 12,
          "end": 12
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "終當如始，不當懈怠。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-15",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 3,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 1
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "聖人欲人所不欲。人欲彰顯，聖人欲伏光；人欲文飾，聖人欲質樸；人欲色，聖人欲於德。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-16",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 3,
          "start": 11,
          "end": 12
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "聖人不眩為服，不賤石而貴玉。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-17",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 3,
          "start": 19,
          "end": 20
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "聖人學人所不能學。人學智詐，聖人學自然；人學治世，聖人學治身；守道真也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-18",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 3,
          "start": 24,
          "end": 25
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "眾人學問反，過本為末，過實為華。復之者，使反本也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-19",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 20,
          "start": 13,
          "end": 13
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "教人反本實者，欲以輔助萬物自然之性也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-20",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 20,
          "start": 13,
          "end": 13
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "聖人動作因循，不敢有所造為，恐遠本也。",
        "source": "cham"
      }
    ],
    "wangbi": [
      {
        "id": "wangbi-1",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 5,
          "start": 8,
          "end": 8
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "雖失無入有，以其微脆之故，未足以興大功，故易也。此四者，皆說慎終也。不可以無之故而不持，不可以微之故而弗散也。無而弗持則生有焉，微而不散則生大焉。故慮終之患，如始之禍，則無敗事。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-2",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 5,
          "start": 8,
          "end": 8
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "謂其安未兆也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-3",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 5,
          "start": 8,
          "end": 8
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "謂微脆也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-4",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 5,
          "start": 8,
          "end": 8
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "當以慎終除微，慎微除亂，而以施為治之，形名執之，反生事原，巧辟滋作，故敗失也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-5",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 16,
          "start": 12,
          "end": 12
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "不慎終也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-6",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 16,
          "start": 12,
          "end": 12
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "好欲雖微，爭尚為之，興難得之貨雖細，貪盜為之起也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-7",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 20,
          "start": 13,
          "end": 13
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "不學而能者，自然也，喻於不學者，過也。故學不學，以復眾人之過。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-8",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 20,
          "start": 13,
          "end": 13
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "",
        "source": "cham"
      }
    ]
  },
