          "range": {
            "type": "range",
            "scope": "verse",
            "verseIndex": 16,
            "start": 12,
            "end": 12
          },
          "kind": "commentary",
          "text": "好欲雖微，爭尚為之，興難得之貨雖細，貪盜為之起也。",
          "source": "cham"
        },
        {
          "id": "wangbi-7",
          "range": {
            "type": "range",
            "scope": "verse",
            "verseIndex": 20,
            "start": 13,
            "end": 13
          },
          "kind": "commentary",
          "text": "不學而能者，自然也，喻於不學者，過也。故學不學，以復眾人之過。",
          "source": "cham"
        },
        {
